      "text": "HW :\nPUSH (S1, 15)\n\nPUSH (S1, 40)\n\nPUSH (S2, 10)\n\nPUSH (S2, POP(S1))\n\nPUSH (S1, POP(S2) - 5)\n\nPUSH (S2, POP(S1) * 2)\n\nPUSH (S1, 50)\n\nPOP (S2)\n\nPUSH (S1, POP(S2))",
