      "originalText": "PUSH (S1, 12)\n\nPUSH (S1, 8)\n\nPUSH (S2, 5)\n\nPUSH (S3, POP(S1) * POP(S2)) \n\nPUSH (S2, POP(S1) + 10) \n\nPUSH (S1, POP(S3) / 2) \nPUSH (S3, 15)\n\nPUSH (S2, POP(S3) - POP(S1))\n\nPUSH (S1, POP(S2))\n\nPOP (S1)\n\nPUSH (S1, POP(S2))",
